Boys is a 2003 Tamil coming-of-age film directed by Shankar. It stars Siddarth, Genelia, Bharath, Nakul and Sai Srinivas Thaman. The score and soundtrack are composed by A. R. Rahman. Wikipedia
Initial release: August 29, 2003
Director: Shankar
Running time: 170 minutes
Music composed by: A. R. Rahman
Screenplay: Sujatha Rangarajan
